You can copy smartSmear source code by commands
git clone https://github.com/smear/parentPOM.git
git clone https://github.com/smear/map-portlet.git
git clone https://github.com/smear/smart.git

You can compile smartSmear by commands
mvn liferay:build-service
mvn package

Maven is available
http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
and requires java. We recommeded to use our operating system package management
to install git (for example: yum install git or apt-get install git)
but without sudo rights be free to download from  
http://git-scm.com/downloads

